Title: Going West
Description:
Leza now walks with the ancestors of this strange land. I must look now to the living.

Kor has led a group of our scouts west deeper into the jungle.

Track him down and lend what aid you can to him. We will join you as quickly as we are able.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Speak with Kor Bloodtusk at Dawnchaser Retreat in the Krasarang Wilds.
